history.content:
A waitlist of 7 people is quite less. Since 189 is known to be a difficult class, many people usually tend to drop it in the first few weeks, although things could be different since this is a summer session (you get charged for dropping lol and you don't have many alternatives).


Edit: there’s a short period (2-3 weeks after the class starts)  where dropping a class gives you a full refund, however, if you want to drop ALL of your classes (assuming the only class you’re taking is 189), then you will be charged. Something to keep in mind
